data.description: Picturesque City in The Hills Two-story home available now for a new homeowner. This newly listed property offers a 2,467 sqft floor plan, one owner, it offers the convenience of a downstairs bedroom and bathroom, making it perfect for guests or multi-generational living. The four spacious bedrooms, including an inviting master bedroom with an en-suite master bathroom, provide ample living space. The backyard features low-maintenance cement, designed to conserve water and reduce upkeep. Plus, a solar system is in place to save both money and energy, ensuring comfortable and eco-friendly living in this spacious home. Enjoy beautiful views and modern amenities in this charming property. Save this one to your favorites and view it today!
